These ten elegant, white tapers bring a sense of a time-honored tradition to your modern farmhouse style. Each candle is individually powered by one CR2025 battery (not included) and includes a built-in timer. The green clip attached to the bottom of each 4.5" taper make it easy to mount them to trees, wreaths, and more. column1: Believe And Merry Christmas Fabric Snowmen - 2/Set
column4:
Believe and Merry Christmas Snowmen is a set of 2 fabric-covered primitive snowmen. These snowmen feature a tall, skinny top hat on their heads and a red felt scarf around their necks. On their bellies is the words "Believe" and "Merry Christmas" simply stitched in red. Both have black stitching for eyes and mouths with orange stitching for a carrot nose. A weighted bottom allows these two adorable snowmen to stand on their own.
Material: Canvas and felt fabrics, metal jingle bells
Size: 9.5" H x 5" W
Weighted bottom for stability

Wish on a Star Snowman is a set of 2 fabric-covered primitive snowmen. One features a skinny top hat with a green felt scarf accented with a metal jingle bell and a sewn-on patch with the words "wish on a star" simply stitched onto his belly. The other features a pipe cleaner candy cane and a sprig of pine attached to her side, along with a red felt scarf and 3 jingle bells attached to her belly. Both have black stitching for eyes and mouths with orange stitching for a carrot nose. A weighted bottom allows these two adorable snowmen to stand on their own.
Material: Canvas and felt fabrics, metal jingle bells
Size: Snowman with top hat: 9.5" H x 3.5" W, Snowman with red scarf: 7" H x 3.75" W
Weighted bottom for stability

This vintage-farmhouse-look, enamel ornament reads "Noel" on a warm-white background. Subtle imperfections in the texture of its spherical shape make it a wonderfully-simple accent this holiday season. Measuring 2.75" high by 2.5" in diameter, including its metal cap, this bauble is topped with a light coat of frosty glitter and hangs by a jute string.

"Joy" is written across the surface of this warm-white, farmhouse-style bauble. It has a handmade, vintage look with subtly-beautiful imperfections in its ceramic texture. Lightly topped with glitter, our Joy White Enamel Ornament hangs by a jute string. Including the metal cap, it measures 2.75" high by 2.5" in diameter.

column1: Merry And Bright White Enamel Ornament
column4: This simple, enamel ornament has a handmade look that fits well with rustic, farmhouse decor. Subtle, charming imperfections on its surface add texture to this spherical adornment that reads "Merry and Bright." Reminiscent of snow, it is topped with glitter and a metal cap, measuring 2.75" high by 2.5" in diameter. Hang it by its jute string hanger from the tree or other floral display this holiday season.

This ornament has a simple, classic look that makes it perfect for farmhouse-inspired holiday decor. Its circular shape has a subtle, handmade texture, dusted with glitter on the top around its metal cap. Measuring 2.75" high by 2.5" in diameter, this enamel ornament hangs by a jute string and reads "Believe."

column1: Jingle All The Way Ceramic Ornament
column4:
Jingle All The Way Ceramic Bell Ornament is a ceramic Christmas ornament of a jingle bell. Bell has a flaxen yellow glazed finish with a green stripe along the top and bottom. The center of the bell is stamped with the phrase, "Jingle all the way," in red script lettering. Hangs on a jute rope cord. Measures 4.5" high by 3.75" wide and .25" deep.
Designer: Dianna Swartz
Materials: Ceramic & jute
Dimensions: 4.5" H x 3.75" W

This ceramic ornament resembles a Christmas cookie decorated with icing! The perfect ornament to bring back those nostalgic memories of Christmases past. Ceramic cutout tree is painted green with red dots for ornaments and the words "Merry & Bright" written in a tan script font with a glaze coating on top. A jute string is attached for hanging.
Material: Ceramic
4" H x 3.5" W (size of ornament only)
Designer: Dianna Swartz

Holly Jolly Ceramic Ornament is a round ceramic Christmas ornament. Ornament has a burgundy glazed background that is stamped with the phrase, "Have a Holly Jolly," in gold lettering. Hangs on a jute cord. Measures 4" in diameter by .25" deep.
Designer: Dianna Swartz
Materials: Ceramic and jute
Dimensions: 4" Dia

This round ceramic ornament is painted ivory with a wreath of watercolor eucalyptus and the phrase "Love grows best in houses just like ours." A glaze coating tops the ornament for a finished look. A jute string is attached for hanging.
Material: Ceramic
4" H x 4" W (size of ornament only)
Designer: Barbara Lloyd

column4:

This red, ceramic bauble is a simple way to bring a vintage feel to your home this Christmas. It has cream-colored lettering on its face that reads "peace," and the top is dusted with glitter. Hang this ornament by its jute twine string and arrange it with like like colors. It measures 2.75" high by 2.5" in diameter. Please note: you must purchase a minimum of 12 for shipping purposes.

Made from smooth, red ceramic our Joy Ornament has vintage appeal. It is embossed with the word, "joy" in cream-colored lettering, and is lightly sprinkled with glitter along the top. Hang this ornament by its jute string to effortlessly give your tree a pop of nostalgia. It measures 2.75" high by 2.5" in diameter. Please note: you must purchase a minimum of 12 for shipping purposes.

In classic Christmas red, this ceramic ornament pops with nostalgia. It has cream-colored lettering on its face that reads, "believe," and the top is sprinkled with glitter. Hang this ornament by its jute twine string to effortlessly give your tree some charm. It measures 2.75" high by 2.5" in diameter. Please note: you must purchase a minimum of 12 for shipping purposes.

Friends and family are nice, but food is everything. Show your guests how you really feel with this white, cotton dish towel that reads, "Merry Christmas Now Let's Eat," in festive red and green lettering. Perfect for drying hands and wiping up spills this towel is a perfect addition to any kitchen this holiday season. Measures 25.5" high by 18" wide.

Everyone knows what happens on Christmas, stays with Christmas. Show your sense of humor with this white, cotton dish towel that reads, "Christmas Calories Don't Count," in festive red and green lettering. Cotton construction ensures durability and absorbency for style and function. Machine-washable and measures 25.5" high by 18" wide.

column1: Fa La La Y'all Dish Towel
column4: Deck your kitchen with a little country charm this Christmas with the Fa La La Y'all dish towel. Taking inspiration from the classic carol, "Deck The Halls," this product reads, "Fa La La Y'all," in festive green and red lettering. Ideal for cleaning any spills this towel is machine-washable and measures 25.5" high by 18" wide.

column1: Eat, Drink, And Be Merry Dish Towel
column4: It's not Christmas without cookies and eggnog! Gift this white, cotton dish towel to your loved ones and remind them to savor the holiday season. Reads, "Eat, Drink, And Be Merry," in red and green lettering and measures 25.5" high by 18" wide.

column1: When I Said I Do Dish Towel
column4: Doing dishes is a drag, but this charcoal gray towel makes it a little better. Cotton construction ensures drying hands and cleaning spills is a breeze and the humorous text reads, "When I Said I Do I Didn't Mean The Dishes." Gift this to newlyweds or hang from your oven for a pop of charm. Measures 25.5" high by 18" wide.

column1: Sorry For The Mess Dish Towel
column4: The Sorry For The Mess Dish Towel comes in charcoal gray and is both stylish and functional due to its cotton construction. Use it to wipe up spills or hang it for display. Reads, "Sorry For The Mess! I Stink At Being A Housewife." Measures 25.5" high by 18" wide.

column4: Featuring a Santa Claus graphic this white, cotton dish towel reads, "I did it all for the cookies," in festive green lettering. Its cotton construction makes it lightweight, durable, and absorbent for a stylish and functional piece. Perfect for the cookie monster inside us all.

This towel measures 28" long x 20" wide, and is a great way to add humor to kitchen decor.

This towel measures 28" long x 20" wide, and is a great way to add humor to kitchen decor.

column1: Let's Get Down And Dirty Dish Towel
column4: Our light grey "Let's Get Down and Dirty" dish towel is a fun variation on a classic farmhouse dishtowel with its embroidered illustration of a dirty martini, which itself is a variation on a classic drink. Not only is the phrasing on this towel clever, but the material is too: with a waffle pattern in the cotton fabric, it has added absorption qualities to it that untextured fabric doesn't. A fabric hanger on the reverse side of the towel allows for easy display.

For the lovers of all things coffee and wine, our "Espresso Then Prosecco" dish towel can be used during any time of day. This towel features a black embroidered illustration of a small espresso cup next to a stemless wine glass on the light grey, waffle patterned surface. The texture of the waffle pattern on the 28" high x 20" wide cotton allows for added absorption qualities of the fabric.

column1: Mamacita Needs A Margarita Dish Towel
column4: When the farmhouse turns into the party house, this light grey, cotton dish towel is there to help clean up the spilled drinks. Reading "Mamacita needs a margarita" and featuring an illustration of a margarita, it is a fun addition to any country-inspired kitchen. Measuring 28" high x 20" wide when opened up with a waffle pattern fabric, it is designed to be more absorbent than an untextured towel.

column1: Wish You Were Beer Dish Towel
column4: From one beer lover to another, this fun light grey, cotton, farmhouse-inspired towel is the perfect addition to any home bar. The black embroidered illustration of two beer steins and the phrase "wish you were beer" is a pun that anyone could appreciate. Measuring 28" high x 20" wide with a waffle pattern that provides added absorption, it is functional as well as stylish.

A light gray cotton dish towel that features an illustration of a coffee cup radiating coffee beans beneath the phrase "but first… coffee" is the perfect blend of modern coffee obsession and a classic country feel. The waffle-textured towel measures 28" high x 20" wide when fully open, includes a fabric hanger on the reverse side, and is embroidered with black and white thread.

column1: I Run On Coffee And Cuss Words Dish Towel
column4: A cotton dish towel in a light grey color that reads "I run on coffee and cuss words" is a fun expression of your love for coffee and profanity in a classically farmhouse medium. Measuring 28" high x 20" wide, this towel depicts coffee through an embroidered illustration of a coffee cup above black and white stripes. The entire towel is made up of a waffle pattern, allowing for added absorption.

column1: We Go Together Like Coffee And Donuts Dishtowel
column4: This gray cotton dishtowel is perfect for your farmhouse coffee bar. With a fun, embroidered illustration of a coffee cup and donuts below the phrase "We go together like coffee and donuts", these textured towels are sure to bring smiles to your country kitchen. When open, this towel measures 28" high x 20" wide and includes a fabric hanger on the reverse side.

column1: Pour Some Sugar On Me Dish Towel
column4: Our "Pour Some Sugar on Me" light grey cotton dish towel, featuring an illustration of a mug of coffee and coffee beans, is perfect for those farmhouse dwellers who just need a bit more sweet coffee and 80's rock music lyrics in their lives. Measuring 28" high x 20" wide with black and white embroidery, it will liven up any country kitchen and have you singing all morning long.

column1: Letters To Santa Post Box, Red
column4: Sit the red Letters to Santa Post Box on an entryway table or mantelpiece to encourage the little ones to get their letters sent off to the North Pole as soon as possible. This beautiful antique-inspired post box features ornate metal work, lightly distressed red paint, a functioning door, and white text that reads "Letters to Santa Post." It measures 15.25" high by 10.5" wide by 4" deep, making it perfect for even the longest of wish lists!

This Christmas Market Mistletoe Enamel Ornament looks great hanging from the branch of a Christmas tree or even from a nail on the wall. With a vintage design, this ornament looks like a road sign straight out of the 1950's. It reads "Christmas Market," "1/2 mile down the road," "open daily until 8," and "meet me under the mistletoe." The separate phrases surround an illustration of a bunch of mistletoe. It hangs from a jute hanger and measures 6.25" in diameter.

The 14.5" Rustic Metal Tree is the medium size in the 3-part series (see items 60278 & 60266.) A bronze-brown base & star topper on the rustic green tree give a subtle nod to the Christmas season that would match any farmhouse Christmas decor.

The 17.75" Rustic Metal Tree is the largest of the 3-piece series (see items 60278 & 60265.) It stands on its own thanks to the bronze-brown base that perfectly matches the star topper on the distressed green tree. Place it on your farmhouse fireplace mantel or in a windowsill to create a beautifully subtle Christmas scene.

The North Pole Planters are a set of 2 different sized galvanized metal planters that feature a festive Christmas design. The smaller planter reads "O Christmas Tree" and measures 13" high by 10.5" wide. The larger of the 2 reads "North Pole" and measures 14.5" high by 12.25" wide. Each planter includes its own red metal stand measuring 5" high and 6" high respectively.

The Merry Christmas Bulb Wall Hanging is a round metal sign that is shaped like a Christmas ornament bulb. This festive piece measures 26.25" high by 23" wide and features dimensional red words that read "Merry Christmas" beneath cut-out holly leaves. The rustic elements of this sign will give some holiday cheer to any living or dining room wall.

Our Happy Pumpkin Season Planter consists of two metal pumpkin cutouts connected by a curved sheet of metal to form a container to house plants. Both pumpkins are embossed with scoring and rounded edges that gives each piece a dimensional look. The phrase "Happy Pumpkin Season," with the letters painted red and orange are also embossed on both pieces. The finishing touch are metal wheels that are attached to the front and back, giving this planter a carriage-like look. This piece puts rustic and fun together to make a great seasonal accent.
Measures 10" H x 6.5" W x 4" D. For indoor use only.

Place pillar candles and florals in the bed of the Winter Pickup Truck to create the perfect winter centerpiece. The distressed red and green paint on the metal truck give just the right amount of festive, rustic flare. It measures 7" high by 14" wide and 5.75" deep.

Remind Santa to remember you on Christmas Eve with the bright red Santa Stop Here Sign. With a mix of green metal and white painted letters, it reads "Santa Stop Here." The Santa Suit design and dimensions of 24" high by 5.5" wide make this sign easily visible from Santa's Sleigh.

column1: Be Merry, Be Bright Street Sign
column4: The Be Merry, Be Bright Street Sign is a great inspirational sign that will remind you of the true meaning of Christmas spirit. With a hole drilled on either end of the sign, it will easily hang on your living room wall next to your Christmas tree or above the row of stockings. It measures 4.75" high by 20.25" wide by 0.75" deep.

The Farm Fresh Trees Metal Tray is a round grey metal tray with worn, soft-white paint. On the base of the tray is a vintage-inspired dimensional design of 3 pine trees and the phrase "farm fresh Christmas trees." Lean this tray next to your stack of firewood in your cozy living room and remind yourself of the time that you found the absolutely perfect Christmas tree.

The 10" Rustic Metal Tree is the smallest of the 3-part series (see items 60265 & 60266.) This freestanding tree has a vintage-inspired look that would accent any country decor perfectly. With its bronze-brown stand and topping star, this tree is a subtle way to show your holiday spirit.

column1: Welcome To Our Farmhouse Post Box
column4:
Our Welcome to Our Farmhouse Post Box is made of galvanized metal that's painted white and distressed throughout with a few rusty spots that give this piece its vintage look. It has a flap top opening, accented with a small knob handle. The words "Welcome of Our Farmhouse," along with a couple of decorative designs are embossed on the front. Two keyhole hooks are on the back for hanging.
Measures 11.5" H x 9" W x 4" D.

column1: Bless You & The Farm Tissue Box
column4:
The Bless You & the Farm Tissue Box is made of galvanized metal that is shaped like a barn. On the front are the black script words that read Bless You & the Farm above the illustration of a barn door.
Materials: Metal
Reads: Bless You & the Farm
7.25" H x 5.75" W x 6" Dp

Distressed wood slats have a clock face painted in ivory with large Roman numerals that says "Old Town Clocks 67 Bailey St." Black metal clock hands and a thick molded wooden frame complete this rustic vintage look. Requires 1 AA battery (not included).
Measures 28" square.

Your customers will love this vintage metal shop sign that has a unique shape and painted gray with white trim and distressed edges. The sign reads: "Oxford Street Antique & Unique Collectibles. Est.1976."
Measures 21" W x 13" H.

A chalkboard with an aged metal frame sits on a decorative metal pedestal and topped with a metal rooster and arrow cutout for a rustic weather vane look.
Measures 16" H x 6" W.

Wood sign measuring 21" W x 5-1/2" H, is painted green with distressing around the edges and displays the words "The Olde Farmhouse" accented with flourishes. The vintage appearance of this sign will add a nostalgic touch to any home decor.

This 7" candle tray is made out of galvanized, smooth metal and is perfect for a pillar candle or a group of votives and tealights. It stands on a wooden pedestal that has been hand-painted white. The pedestal measures 7.5" high. This would look lovely with any country or farmhouse decor, or with a mantel or centerpiece arrangement.

column3: (All) The Hearthside Collection|Frames & Table Decor|Tabletop|Vintage Home
column4: This vintage clock is shaped like an old-fashioned produce scale, with the bowl on top as a separate piece. The glass covered clock face is old-world style, with Roman numerals, French accents and a tea-stained distressed look. The scale is painted a distressed black, and the bowl on top of the scale is removable with a diameter of 8 inches. The total size of this clock is 10" high by 6-3/4" wide by 7-1/2" deep. Clock runs on quartz timing and requires 1 AA battery (not included).

Our Gather in Our Kitchen Sign is a wood plank sign with a light brown wooden frame printed with the following phrase:
Come Gather in Our Kitchen
sit long, talk much, laugh often
Sign measures 24" wide by 6" high by 1" deep. Two metal d-ring hooks are on either side in back for hanging.

Measuring 7" high x 15 ¼" wide x ¼" deep, this seasonal wall art hangs by two sawtooth hangers and reads "Southern Pine," "Christmas tree," and "fresh cut free delivery." "Christmas tree" is written in playful script and set next to a red-and-green illustration of a truck carrying a pine tree. The printed edges of this enameled sign convey an antiqued, rusty look that brings vintage style to holiday decor.

Accent farmhouse and rustic decor with our Round Tobacco Basket. Its simple, tobacco-style woven texture makes it ideal for display on a wall or tabletop. The basket measures 17 ¾" in diameter x 3 ⅛" deep. Floral sold separately.

column3: (All) The Hearthside Collection|Frames & Table Decor|Tabletop|Vintage Home
column4:
Standing 7" tall x 16 ¼" wide x 8" deep, our Antique Decorative Scale w/ Clock makes a statement in any home with its antiqued look. This metal scale has a textured, gray-and-black brushed finish whose subtlety compliments the clock face that sits in place of a gage. The clock face has an aged look with spots that have been tarnished with rust, completed by intricate die-cut hands. It opens at the back and takes one AA battery, not included.

Please note: for decorative use only. This product is not intended to be used with food. Floral sold separately.

Our Laundry Co. Distressed Metal Sign freshens up the laundry room with its crisp, vintage look. It reads "Laundry Co," "wash・dry・fold・press," and "same day service" in black lettering on a white background. The edges have a worn metal look and the appearance of rust at the borders. This wall art measures 10 ¼" tall x 13 ¾" wide x ¼" deep and hangs from two sawtooth hangers.

column1: The Olde Milk & Creamery Distressed Metal Sign
column4: Measuring 13 ¾" tall x 10 ¼" wide x ¼" deep, this wall art brings the kitchen to life with its crisp, vintage look. The edges have a worn metal appearance, and the look of weathered rust around the border. This enamel art hangs from two sawtooth hangers and reads "The Olde Milk and Creamery," "fresh dairy since 1889," "daily delivery service," and "hand churned butter" in black lettering on either side of the silhouette of a cow on a white background.

The Butcher's Guide Distressed Metal Sign reads "the butcher's guide" above silhouetted, diagrammed illustrations of a chicken, pig, and cow. This enamel wall art measures 13 ¾" tall x 10 ¼" wide x ¼" deep and hangs from two sawtooth hangers. Its simple, black-and-white color scheme and worn appearance livens up any farmhouse kitchen.

Our Laundry Rules Distressed Metal Sign is a perfect laundry-room accessory, with its themed imagery and text. This enamel wall art has a black-and-white color scheme and a weathered, rusted appearance at its edges. It measures 13 ¾" tall x 10 ¼" wide x ¼" deep and hangs from two sawtooth hangers.

Our Farmhouse Tobacco Basket reads "farmhouse" at the center of a rectangular tobacco-style basket. The natural wood color of the woven pieces compliments the painted-white, wood lettering that sits at the center of the basket. Hang this decorative piece on a wall in the living room or other gathering space to bring the room together. This basket measures 10 ½" tall x 18" wide x 2 ½" deep.

column1: Galvanized Metal Farm Sweet Farm Sign
column4: Measuring 7" tall x 32 ¼" wide x ½" deep, this galvanized metal wall art hangs by two keyhole hangers and reads "farm sweet farm" in raised lettering with a hand-painted appearance. The rust-colored paint that lines the text has also been brushed over the border's edges to create a rusty look. The rustic, hand-made look of this wall art makes it a perfect piece to hang in family gathering spaces.

column1: Kitchen Is For Dancing Distressed Metal Sign
column4: This distressed metal sign's black-and-white color palette and fun, graphic appeal energizes kitchen decor. The border of this enamel wall art has a distressed, rust look, and its text reads "this kitchen is for dancing," accented on either side by a wheat motif. It measures 13 ¾" tall x 10 ¼" wide x ¼" deep and hangs from two sawtooth hangers.

column1: Farmhouse Gray Perpetual Calendar And Scale
column3: (All) The Hearthside Collection|Frames & Table Decor|Tabletop|Vintage Home
column4:
This simple, vintage-look metal scale has been painted light gray. The removable dish has a black border accent at its rim that plays off of the chipped black accents at the edges of the the scale. A distressed calendar sits in place of a gauge and reads "vintage 1897 farmhouse" in black text. This scale stands 14" tall x 9 ½" wide x 10 ¼" deep and looks great on any countertop or shelf in the kitchen.
Please note: for decorative use only. This product is not intended to be used with food. Floral sold separately.

column1: Housework Won't Kill You Distressed Metal Sign
column4: This wall art reads "housework won't kill you but why take the chance" in white lettering on a black, textured background with weathered edges that have a rust look. Its humorous phrase brightens the feel of home decor in any room. It measures 10 ⅜" high x 13 ¾" wide x ¼" deep and hangs from two sawtooth hangers.

column1: Black And Galvanized Metal Baking Co. Enamel Sign
column4: Measuring 7 ¼" tall x 19" wide, this vintage-inspired wall art reads "Baking Co premium baked goods" over a black enamel background. The enamel on the lettering has been sanded away to reveal the shine of bare metal. This simple sign hangs by two sawtooth hangers and brings a fresh antique look to the kitchen.

column1: Olde Suffolk Woolen Mills Sheep Drawstring Bag
column4:
Olde Suffolk Woolen Mills Sheep Drawstring Bag is a drawstring burlap sack that features a sheep illustration and the words, "The Olde Suffolk Woolen Mills. Spring Thyme Blend. Hand washed wool."
Bag measures 9.25" high by 6.75" wide and .25" deep.

column1: Basket Weave Two-Level Round Wall Shelf
column4: The unique shape of this stylish round shelf brings a fresh look to modern farmhouse decor. The classic, basket weave has a gray wash and its two 4.25" deep shelves are great for holding your favorite decorative finds and trinkets. Overall, the shelf measures 20" in diameter. The space between shelves is 8" high, with a maximum height of 6" above the top shelf and below the bottom shelf. Mount it to your statement wall or around the home by the attached sawtooth hanger.

column1: Bless This Home Distressed Metal Sign
column4: "Bless this home," reads this square, metal sign. It has an aged, rust-like look at its edges that frames text encircled by leaf motifs. Place this sign in the kitchen or on a feature wall in the home to add a sense of vintage, farmhouse style. It measures 12" square x .25" deep and includes two sawtooth hangers for convenient wall mounting.

column1: Home Sweet Home White Metal Wall Sign
column4: Add a vintage touch to your farmhouse style with this white metal sign. It reads "home sweet home" in raised, curly and classic lettering, balanced on either side by a leaf motif. A thin border compliments the rounded metal edges of this 8" high x 18" wide x .25" deep black-and-white wall accent. Two sawtooth hangers make it easy to mount in the kitchen, living room, or elsewhere in the home.

column1: Grateful Black And White Metal Street Sign
column4: The clean, black-and-white look of this dimensional metal street sign bring vintage style and charm to the everyday farmhouse. It reads "grateful" in script lettering and has a hand-painted-look border. Hang this 4.25" high x 20" wide x .25" deep accent easily by two sawtooth hangers in the living room, kitchen, or laundry room.

column1: Thankful Black And White Metal Street Sign
column4: The simplicity of this dimensional metal street sign reads "thankful" in script lettering. A charming accent for the everyday farmhouse, it brings vintage inspiration to any room with its street sign shape and hand-painted-style border. It can hang by two sawtooth hangers in the living room, kitchen, or entryway of the home and measures 4.25" high x 20" wide x .25" deep.

column1: Together Is Our Favorite Place To Be Metal Wall Sign
column4: "Together is our favorite place to be," reads this black-and-white metal sign. The text is a combination of distressed script and typewriter lettering, encircled by vine and leaf illustrations. It hangs by two sawtooth hangers with ease and measures 12" square x .25" deep.

column1: The Laundry Co. Vintage Hanging Sign
column4: Introduce classic, vintage style to your farmhouse. This 4" high x 10" wide x .25" deep hanging sign features the phrase "The Laundry Co." along with additional laundry-themed text. The metal is painted white and features an embossed, decorative border. Hang this stylish piece on the wall or from a doorknob or cabinet using the attached, black wire hanger.

column1: Rustic White Decorative Scale With Clock
column4:
Rustic White Decorative Scale with Clock features lightly distressed, white painted metal with a chipped paint finish. Includes a removable tray that can be used to hold decorative items for the kitchen or dining room. A working clock is attached to the front of the scale which requires 1 AA battery (not included).
Measures 10.25" high by 8.5" wide and 9.5" deep.
Please note: item is for decorative use only. Scale is not functional. Do not use with food.

column1: As For Me And My House Metal Cutout Sign
column4:
As For Me and My House Cutout Metal Sign is a rustic metal sign that has been brushed with a distressed finish for an aged, weather-worn look. Sign features cut out lettering in a stencil-style font that displays the biblical passage, "As for me & my house, We will serve the lord. - Joshua 24:15." Sign has four pre-drilled holes, one in each corner, for wall hanging or mounting purposes.
Measures 19.25" wide by 14" high.

Farmers Market Distressed Metal Sign is made of galvanized metal with a lightly rusted finish. Featuring black painted embossed lettering, the sign reads: Farmers Market - Dairy Produce • Dry Goods. With an ornate, vintage-style shape, this sign also includes four pre-drilled holes for hanging or mounting.
Measures 23" wide by 6.5" high and .25" deep.

column1: Made With Love Distressed Metal Kitchen Sign
column4:
Made with Love Distressed Metal Kitchen Sign is made of galvanized metal with a lightly rusted finish. Featuring black painted embossed lettering, the sign reads: Kitchen - Always Fresh • Made With Love. With an ornate, vintage-style shape, this sign also includes four pre-drilled holes for hanging or mounting.
Measures 23" wide by 6.5" high and .25" deep.

column3: (All) The Hearthside Collection|2021 Products|Everyday Decor|Frames & Table Decor
column4: The simplistic style of this white metal shelf sitter makes it an easy farmhouse accessory on a mantel, table, or scenic windowsill. The word "home" is written in contemporary script lettering, set inside a circle of silhouetted leaves on a vine. It stands on a hinged, wire easel and measures 4.25" diameter x .25" deep.

column1: White Vintage Hanging Decorative Scale W/Clock
column4: Make a statement in your classic farmhouse with our vintaged, white metal, decorative scale with clock. Featuring a functional clock with an easy-open back that runs on one AA battery, it suspends a removable metal basket. Hang it in your kitchen from the attached metal hook as a creative way to display artificial produce, cookbooks, or your favorite florals and candles. Assembled, it measures 33" high x 12.25" wide x 10.5" deep.

column1: Olive Bucket File Organizer W/Envelope Pouch
column4: This galvanized metal, farmhouse-chic file organizer features olive-bucket style dividers and a dimensional envelope-shaped pouch. It stands 8.25" square x 10.25" deep. Add this to your office space as a creative addition to your functional decor.

column1: Framed Love Sign With Metal Cutout
column4: A stained wood border frames the word "love" cut out of a white, painted-wood panel. A sheet of galvanized metal is mounted at the back, showing through the cutout letters to create a subtle, farmhouse-perfect look. This small sign comes with an attached sawtooth hanger and is perfect for your feature wall and measures 8" square x 1" deep.

This small, farmhouse-chic sign reads "relax" in script cutout lettering on a wood board. A sheet of galvanized metal is mounted behind the letters so that it shows through to the front. Framed by a whitewashed-wood border, this 8" squared x 1" deep sign makes a great addition to a feature wall or the wall above a fireplace. It hangs easily by one sawtooth hanger.

column1: Thankful, Grateful, Blessed Metal Cutout Sign
column4: The Thankful, Grateful, Blessed Metal Sign is made of galvanized metal and resembles a large plate in shape with a flat back and curved rim. It features a lightly distressed trim and a laser cutout of the phrase, "Thankful, Grateful, Blessed," along with a decorative leaf wreath. A sawtooth hanger in back allows for easy hanging. Measures 14.5" in diameter by 1.5" deep.

column1: The Gathering Place White Coaster Set
column4: Our Gathering Place coaster set features four white, tile coasters with different inspiring phrases to uplift your farmhouse style. They each showcase different vine and branch patterns that encircle these phrases. Each has a distressed, uniquely chipped look with a cork bottom. Stacked, they measure 1.75" high x 4" square.

Our round basket weave coffee table has a classic, woven texture painted with a gray wash to give it a refreshing, farmhouse style. The basket top measures 4.5" high with a diameter of 23.25" and sits in a conveniently collapsible base made of black metal. Overall it stands 20.25" high x 23.25, making it a perfect size for any living room or den.

Our set of two Tobacco Baskets make a classic addition to farmhouse decor. These can be mounted to the wall or placed out on a table, where their dark-washed wooden texture adds a rustic element to the home.
The baskets measure 23 ½" tall x 14 ¾" wide and 20 ½" tall x 13 ½" wide.

This festive and weathered Joy Enamel Wall Sign features the word "Joy" spelled out in white lettering, with the "o" in the middle replaced by a snowflake. The paint of the metal sign has been artfully chipped to compliment the bright red enamel background and measures 10 ¼" tall x 20 ½" wide x ½" deep.

Our White Enamel Windmill Clock mounts well to any wall in the home, measuring 33" in diameter x 2" deep. This vintage-inspired clock resembles a windmill and has been weathered to a classic black-and-white palette, while the style of the lettering and hands are reminiscent of classic country decor.

column3: (All) The Hearthside Collection|Frames & Table Decor|Tabletop|Vintage Home
column4: Add a vintage-inspired classic to your kitchen decor with our Rustic White Scale. This metal scale measures 8" tall x 17 ¾" wide x 7 ¾ " deep. The weathered paint reveals a rustic texture, and the simple trays are a perfect way to display votive candles, tea lights, or florals. Floral and votive candle sold separately.

Our Glass Flower Jar consists of a mason jar seated in a rustic wire caddy. This farmhouse accent is great for displaying flowers or your favorite artificial floral around the home.
Measures 7" high x 4 ¼" wide x 4" deep. Floral sold separately.

Tobacco baskets have become a hot decorating item! Our woven baskets are made of a dark-washed wood and are great for displaying artificial florals or even as wall decor for a chic farmhouse look.
This set of three includes baskets measuring 17 ¼" in diameter, 15 ¼" in diameter, and 13" in diameter.
Florals not included.

The corrugated and aged metal of this Floral Wall Hanging provides a backdrop for a simple glass jar that is held up by a rusty metal band. This dimensional rustic piece can be paired with flowers or artificial florals to add texture and a fresh farmhouse feel in any room.
Measures 19" tall x 9" wide x 3 ½" deep. Cotton floral sold separately.

Our Farm Fresh Trees Wooden Sign is stained and has a natural wood grain. Notches are cut out at the top to give this sign a wood slat look. It features a green corrugated metal cutout of a pine tree with the words "Farm Fresh Christmas Trees, Pine Fir Spruce Cedar," printed on the sign. Two sawtooth hangers are on back. This sign is the perfect accent for a country Christmas!
Measures 21.5" high by 14" wide.

Our vintage-style Farmhouse Truck is painted bright red with weathered distressing to expose metal and rust. This piece can inspire feelings of days gone by and would make a great retro accent to any room of the home.
It measures 10" high x 22" wide x 10.25" deep.

This set of 3 nesting decorative containers are fashioned into the shape of vintage farm silos. Made of aged metal, the body of each silo is painted white and aged with rust. The silos measure 10" tall x 7.5" in diameter; 8" tall x 5.5" in diameter,and 12.5" tall x 8.25" in diameter.

This classic vintage sleigh is made of metal and has an old-time rustic style with it's chipped red paint and scrolling features. It's the perfect piece to display Christmas florals or candy and adds a touch of "Christmases Past" to any room!
Sleigh stands 13" high x 23 ½" wide x 11" deep with inside dimensions of 10" high x 17" wide x 9" deep. Floral not included.

Shaped similar to sleighs from earlier times, this piece will certainly bring a vintage feel to any Christmas decor. The body of the sleigh is aged, galvanized metal, bordered by thick metal wire which makes up the curling details of the sleigh and skis. It measures 10.75" tall by 9.75" wide by 14.5" deep.
Requires assembly.

Place this decorative metal pulley around the home and let its weathered rustic flair pull the room together. It measures 34" high x 7" wide x 2.5" deep and hangs from a jute rope. The pulley has a hook at the bottom and looks well by itself, or can hold other hanging decorations

Celebrate vintage, country style with our enameled windmill wall clock. White blades are arranged around a black center with two clock hands to resemble an old-fashioned windmill. Four numbers are arranged around this 14" diameter x 2" deep clock. It operates on one AA battery (not included) and hangs easily in the living room, kitchen, or around the home by the attached keyhole hanger.

column1: Hanging Scale W/ Two Wire Baskets
column4:
The rustic style and aged look of this metal hanging scale is perfect for any farmhouse-inspired home. A printed gage with measurements is adhered below the scale's fulcrum and each arm features hooks that support two removable, 6" high x 12.75" diameter, metal-wire baskets. Use it to creatively display artificial fruit, decorative pillows, or plants and florals. Assembled, it measures 34.5" high x 36" wide x 12.75" deep and hangs by a hook at the top.

Please note: for decorative use only. This product is not intended to be used with food. Florals sold separately. Items pictured used as props.

Place this set of three woven baskets around the home to enhance its industrial farmhouse style. Each one has an open weave with a round top and square base. They feature a decorative, galvanized metal band and two rustic, jute rope handles. Each size measures 8" high x 20.25" in diameter, 7" high x 19" in diameter, and 6.75" high x 15.25" in diameter.

The Joy Wreath Wall Hanging is a 3-piece metal sign that when placed together spell the word "Joy." Because the letters are separate in this way, they are able to be hung in any orientation. The distressed red paint on the "J" and "Y" accent the green of the wreath "O" and help to give this sign a vintage feel. As a whole, it measures 10.5" high by 24" wide.

Place this decorative Santa Suit Mug next to your coffee maker and fill it with your favorite florals, candle, or unusable coffee beans. The distressed mug is designed with red paint, white paint trim, and a black belt just like Santa's classic suit. It measures 4.75" high by 4.75" in diameter. Though this mug isn't food grade, it would bring some holiday cheer to your morning routine when you see it sitting in your kitchen.
Please note: This item is for decorative use only and is not food safe.

The Joy Snowman Hanger is made from flat galvanized metal accented with a red painted corrugated metal scarf. He features cut outs that include the snowman's face and hat details, a holly leaf, and the word "JOY." Hung from a natural jute rope hanger.
Materials: Metal and Jute
17.25" H x 4.5" W

The Noel Snowman Hanger is made from flat galvanized metal accented with a green painted corrugated metal scarf. He features cut outs that include the snowman's face and hat details, a holly leaf, and the word "NOEL." Hung from a natural jute rope hanger.
Materials: Metal and jute
17.25" H x 4.75" W

Place your favorite artificial plants and candles in the Buffalo Check Metal Basket to create a centerpiece for your farmhouse table. The Red Buffalo Check pattern and rustic elements make this basket perfect for any time of year. It measures 7" high by 14.5" wide by 9" deep.

The Joy Windmill Metal Plaque is the perfect blend of Christmas and farmhouse decor! The word "Joy" is cut from red painted metal, with a galvanized windmill in the center in place of the letter "O". It Measures 5" high by 10.25" wide and has a metal hanger on the back.
Materials: Metal
Dimensions: 5" H x 10.25" W

Noel Windmill Metal Plaque features red painted letters that have been cut from metal that spell out the word "Noel". A galvanized metal windmill is displayed in place of the letter "O" for a unique farmhouse look. It measures 5" high by 13.25" wide and has a metal hanger on the back.
Materials: Metal
Dimensions: 5" H x 13.25" W
Windmill Design

column1: White Vintage Snowflake Buckets - Set Of 4
column4: The White Vintage Snowflake Buckets are nesting buckets that each feature a unique cutout snowflake design. They are grey metal with distressed white paint and are held by a rusty handle.These rustic buckets range in size from 8.75" high by 7" in diameter to 5.75" high by 4.75" in diameter, making them the perfect containers for winter candles and florals.

Add the Merry Christmas Buffalo Check Ornament to your Christmas wall decorations for a unique touch of color and festive cheer. Measuring 15.5" high by 13.5" wide by 0.25" deep, the bulb-shaped ornament features the red buffalo check design, a silver metal top, and a natural jute rope hanger. Written in a classically Christmas font is the phrase "Merry Christmas to all" next to an illustration of holly leaves and berries.

Home Pride Coffee Clock is a retro diner-style clock that features a coffee logo that reads:
"Home Pride Coffe
Premium Quality
Freshly Roasted
Since 1909"
Color is ivory with a slight tea stained vintage look. Measures 13" in diameter. Requires 1 AA battery (not included).

Rise & Shine Farms Clock is an exclusive illustration by Dianna Swartz featuring the words "Rise & Shine Farms" along with a white rooster. Clock color is black with light distressing. The perfect clock for any country kitchen! Made of pressed wood. Measures 13" in diameter. Requires 1 AA battery (not included).

Our 13-inch pressed wood clock is off-white with a colorful image of a bushel of apples and the words "Apples Picked Daily" in the center. Large numbers, black clock hands and overall distressing accent this clock to give it an old world rustic feel. Clock workings are quartz and take one AA battery (not included). Keyhole opening in back for hanging.

Our 13-inch pressed wood clock is off-white with black decorative details around the edge. The center of the clock reads:
HOME
Where you treat your friends like family,
and your family like friends.
1889
Large numbers, black clock hands and overall tea stain distressing accent this clock to give it an old world rustic feel. Clock workings are quartz and take one AA battery (not included). Keyhole opening in back for hanging.

Our battery-operated timer pillar measures 3" x 3 1/2" and is an ivory/cinnamon color.
This candle has two separate “on" functions. By switching the switch to the “1" position, the timer pillar will remain on until you turn it off. By switching the switch to the “2" position, the timer function is activated.
The timer function means the candle stays on for 6 hours, goes off for 18 hours, and then automatically turns back on for another 6 and off for 18, and so on. The time that you originally flip the switch to the “2" position will be the time it comes on each day. If you wish to reset the timer, turn the candle off and back on at the time you wish for them to be set.

column4:

Directions:
Our timer pillars have two separate “on" functions. By switching to the “1" position, the timer pillar will remain on until you turn it off. By switching to the “2" position, the timer function is activated.

The timer function means the candle stays on for 6 hours, goes off for 18 hours, and then automatically turns back on to repeat the cycle. The time that you originally flip the switch to the “2" position will be the time it comes on each day. If you wish to reset the timer, turn the candle off and back on at the desired time.

Liberty Annie is a primitive doll measuring approx. 21" in height. Annie is adorned with a rusty bell, moss, and an American Flag.
Christmas Annie Doll is wearing a felt Santa suit decorated with rusty bells, pip berries, greenery, and a plaid scarf. Christmas Annie is approx. 22" tall.

Jackson Spindle Scarecrow measures approximately 17-3/4" H and 7" W. Jackson is adorned with a sunflower, straw, and a burlap hat. He sits atop a black spindle.

Designed by Kitty Johnson

Fabric Scarecrow Head decorated with straw, a burlap hat, jute rope, and a plaid scarf. Scarecrow sits atop a wooden stake. Measures 15" H and 4" W.

Designed by Kitty Johnson

The Snowman Head Pick measures 16-1/2" H with a diameter of 3". A fabric snowman head sits atop a wooden stake and is adorned with plaid fabric, a rusty bell, and a snowy, black top hat.


Designed by Kitty Johnson

Chris Snowman measures approximately 16" H (while sitting, 25" total height) x 11.5" wide x 8.5" deep. Chris is wearing a plaid scarf, mittens, a snowy top hat, and is complete with a long carrot nose. Candy canes and Christmas greenery are attached to his arm.

Designed by Kitty Johnson

Max Ornament measures approximately 5" H and 2" in diameter. Max comes complete with a snowy top hat, a scarf, and long legs for easy displaying in your winter decor!

Designed by Kitty Johnson

One of the dolls in our Sprinkles collection, Songbook is a self-standing snowman donning a red hat and scarf and holding a songbook printed with musical notes and trimmed in pine that is attached to both arms. As the name entails, Stockings is finished off with a "sprinkle" of glitter for a luminous glow. Stands at 8-1/2" tall.

Red wool mitten with a tweed pattern and a fleece cuff has a little brown mouse inside wearing a Santa hat. Some greenery and holly berries are nestled beside him. Has a string in the back for hanging. Can be hung as an ornament or as part of a special addition to any holiday decor. Measures 8" tall. Designed by Joyce Napotnik.

Liberty Mouse is a fabric-covered mouse with fabric-covered wire arms and bead eyes. He's wearing a red plaid bow tie and holding an American flag. A craft paper tag with his name on it is attached to him with a safety pin. A weighted bottom allows sitting stability. He stands 6" tall. Designed by Joyce Napotnik.

Our Holly Doll is a unique design by artist Joyce Napotnik. She has big blue eyes and is wearing a red plaid dress with lace details. Her look is finished with a matching bow in her hair made of ivory yarn. She has her toy doll tucked in her arm and has floppy arms and legs. A weighted bottom makes her easy to sit.
Holly Doll measures 20" tall by 6" wide.

Our Baby Bug Doll is a unique design by artist Joyce Napotnik. Her primitive face has big green eyes and she's wearing a red plaid dress decorated with a lace collar. Her look is finished off with an adorable bonnet tied with plaid strips that match her dress. She's got a stuffed lady bug attached to her floppy arm with a rusty wire. Her legs are bent at the knees so she can sit "criss cross applesauce" and she has a weighted bottom for stability.
Baby Bug measures 17" tall by 6" wide.
Rusty metal cutout of a heart is decorated with a distressed American flag design. A metal wire is attached for hanging. Measures 11" H x 9" W.

Our windmill is made of galvanized metal and has rusty edges for a distressed look. Metal hanger on back.
Measures 14" in diameter
For the bird lover, this tealight holder has a natural wood base and a rusty tin bird cutout attached. Measures 4" tall and 2-1/2" in diameter.
For the bird lover, this tealight holder has a natural wood base with a rusty tin bird that's perched on a branch attached. Measures 7" tall and 2-1/2" in diameter.
Frog Critter is a fabric covered frog with hand-painted details and the phrase "Kiss Me" on its belly. A weighted bottom gives stability when sitting. Measures 7" high by 4" wide.

Bee Critter is a fabric covered bee with hand-painted details, black antennas and fabric covered wings. He's wearing a string collar that has the words "Bee Happy" hand written on a paper tag. A weighted bottom gives stability when sitting. Measures 7" high by 6" wide.

Dragon Fly Critter is a fabric covered dragon fly with hand-painted details, black antennas and fabric covered wings. He's wearing a string collar that has the words "Fly with Me" hand written on a paper tag. A weighted bottom gives stability when sitting. Measures 6" high by 7" wide.

Presents Mouse is a primitive mouse doll wearing a red plaid scarf. Self-standing, Presents Mouse has a long curved tail and he's holding a Christmas present and a candy cane in his hands. A craft paper tag with his name on it finishes off this festive piece. Measures 6" H x 2-1/2" W.

A set of 6 santa hats made of felt fabric and accented with a pine and berry trim and a rusty metal bell. A simple plastic string is attached for hanging. Each ornament measures 3-3/4" wide by 2-1/2" high.

Lady Bug is part of our Lil' Buddies Collection. She's covered in black felt fabric with red, polka-dot wings attached to her back. On her head are wire antennas and black bead eyes. She is holding a red berry in her hand and she's got a craft paper name tag attached by a safety pin. Her feet are implanted in a plaster base and she stands 9" tall.

His legs and arms are covered in green felt and he is carrying a bunch of hay in one arm and a black bat on a wire attached to the other arm. His feet are implanted into a plaster base. Tiny metal stars accent his front. This primitive piece will look great with any rustic Halloween decor!

She is wearing a green gingham jumper with button accents and she's holding a stuffed slice of watermelon in her hands. Her burgundy yarn hair is pulled into pigtails. She's got large blue painted-on eyes and she's wearing a craft paper name tag pinned to her dress. A weighted bottom gives her stability when sitting. Mandy is just as adorable as can be!
Measures 18" high.

column1: Icy Mixed Pine Pick W/ Cone 13"
column4: Dusted in a light frost, this 13" seasonal pick pairs artificial mixed pine needles with a pine cone accent. This Icy Mixed Pine Pick brings the rustic, natural essence of winter to life in seasonal displays for the home.

column1: Glittered Mixed Pine Pick W/ Cone 13"
column4: Our 13" Glittered Mixed Pine Pick w/ Cone brings the rustic, natural essence of winter to life in home decor. Realistic artificial mixed pine needles are dusted with glitter and paired with a pine cone accent.

The soft blue hues in this set of six decorative eggs placed in a gray carton bring freshness to nature-inspired displays. These eggs are hollow, and made of a lightweight, Styrofoam-like material.
The carton measures 3" tall x 10" wide x 4" deep.

The 8" high Icy Tahoe Spray has a morning frost look on the short green sprigs with small pinecones scattered through them. Add to your natural outdoor seasonal decor or bring a bit of nature inside with this evergreen winter accent.

Complete your winter decor with 15" Mountain Pine Pick. Unlike a real snowy pine tree branch, the snow won't melt away, the needles won't litter your floor, and the stems won't dry out. Standing 15" tall, this pick will look great among any other wintery florals or inside a vase to show your love of the season.

The 12" Icy Tahoe Tree is a freestanding artificial tree that is the perfect for the frosty winter months. As a smaller version of item F10040, they look great as a pair. However, this artificial evergreen is a great winter accent on its own.

Add a bit of greenery to your winter decor with the Icy Evergreen Tahoe Tree. This 9" tall, freestanding, artificial tree features frosted leaves and pinecones throughout the branches and stands on a natural wood slice base.

This mini tree is comprised of glittered plastic pine needles and pinecones to give it the look of having been out in a winter ice storm. A weight is cleverly hidden beneath the burlap to help the tree stand on its own. It measures 16" high.

The Glittered Pinecone Tree is an artificial, freestanding floral that is comprised of heavily glittered foam greenery, small pinecones, a natural branch trunk, and a solid square base. It is easily sat on any flat surface for display and measures 8" high with a 2" square base.

column1: Bless This Home Crow Timer Pillar
column3: (All) The Hearthside Collection|2021 Products|LED Candles & Tapers|Primitive Home
column4:
This is our 3" x 4-1/2" wave-top pillar candle that features a grungy textured wax coating on the outside, and a smooth wax coating on the inside with a flame shaped amber lightbulb. There is an area on the pillar where the textured coating is smoothed out and the words "Bless This Home" along with a crow silhouette with a primitive star hanging from its beak are printed on the candle.
Directions:
Our timer pillars have two separate “on" functions. By switching to the “1" position, the timer pillar will remain on until you turn it off. By switching to the “2" position, the timer function is activated.

The timer function means the candle stays on for 6 hours, goes off for 18 hours, and then automatically turns back on to repeat the cycle. The time that you originally flip the switch to the “2" position will be the time it comes on each day. If you wish to reset the timer, turn the candle off and back on at the desired time.

There is an area on the pillar where the textured coating is smoothed out and the words "Sing to the Lord with a thankful heart. Col. 3:16," along with a bird on a tree branch are printed on the candle.
Directions:
Our timer pillars have two separate “on" functions. By switching to the “1" position, the timer pillar will remain on until you turn it off. By switching to the “2" position, the timer function is activated.

The timer function means the candle stays on for 6 hours, goes off for 18 hours, and then automatically turns back on to repeat the cycle. The time that you originally flip the switch to the “2" position will be the time it comes on each day. If you wish to reset the timer, turn the candle off and back on at the desired time.

This version of Santa is wearing a primitive outfit that is contrasted with a bright red scarf and hat that hangs down his side. The doll can either lean on something or hang from a small string on its back for display. It was designed by Dawn Stake and measures 16" high by 9.5" wide and 2" deep.

The Lori Doll is a primitive girl doll that is wearing a dark plaid dress, a straw hat, and black shoes with white laces. Under her arm is a stem of a beautiful artificial brown sunflower and she wears a tag pinned to her with her name printed on it. She is weighted so she can sit on her own on a shelf or chair. This doll was designed by Dawn Stake and measures 22" high by 7.5" wide and 3" deep.

The Grandpa Martin Doll is a primitive man doll that looks like the classic vintage grandpa. He has white cotton hair on the sides of his bald head, his eyebrows, and mustache. He wears a simple striped shirt, a thick fluffy scarf, and denim colored fabric pants. There are thin wire glasses on his face and a tag pinned to his scarf that reads Martin and he carries a yellowed newspaper. The Grandpa Martin doll is weighted so he can sit up on his own on a shelf or in a chair. This doll was designed by Kitty Johnson and measures 16" high by 4.5" wide and 2" deep.
Shown with item number CS37633 Grandma Nellie Doll.

The Grandma Nellie Doll is a primitive woman doll that looks like a classic vintage grandma. She is wearing black wire glasses, an off white dress with pink stars and a lighter pink collar, and has curly grey yarn hair. Pinned to her dress is a tag printed with the name Nellie, and she's carrying a ball of yarn with a a tapestry needle held in it. This doll was designed by Kitty Johnson and measures 17" high by 5" wide and 2" deep.
Shown with item # CS37629 Grandpa Martin Doll and item # CS37680 Little Nellie Grandma Doll

The Chilly Snowman Doll is a freestanding plush snowman figure with stitched facial features, a fabric top hat and scarf, and a bundle of artificial winter florals. Pinned to his scarf is a name tag that reads Chilly. This adorable snowman would perfectly accent any winter decor. It was designed by Joyce Napotnik and measures 9.5" high by 4" wide and 3" deep.
Pictured with item number CS37699, Chilly Snowman Ornament.

The Cozy Scarf Snowman Stake is a twig stake that is topped by a rustic, plush snowman. The snowman is an off white color with two black buttons on its stomach and a red fabric scarf around its neck. The snowman also has dimensional facial features and a twig crown on its head. This snowman stake was designed by Dawn Stake and measures 14" high by 2" wide and 2" deep.

The Charlie Snowman Doll is a vintage looking plush snowman that is the perfect piece to welcome your friends to your home during the holiday season. The snowman is wearing a matching knit hat and scarf with a striped pattern and is carrying on its twig arm a lightly distressed wood sign on a metal wire that reads Welcome Friends next to illustrations of a star and a stocking. Pinned to the scarf is a name tag that reads Charlie. This adorable snowman was designed by Joyce Napotnik and measures 10.5" high by 7" wide and 7" deep.

The Antique Carrot is a foam carrot covered in orange dyed fabric that has been lightly distressed for an antique look. A piece of natural jute rope is tied around the middle to allow you to hang it or attach it to other decor pieces. At the top of the carrot are strands of straw tucked into the fabric for a natural look. This carrot was designed by Dawn Stake and measures 12" high by 2.5" wide and 0.5" deep.

The Americana Heart Ornaments are an assortment of two different designs that will show your American pride in a subtle way. Each design features the American flag image on a fabric heart base, one is printed vertically while the other is horizontal. They hang from a thin black hanger and measure 4" high by 2.5" wide.

The Candy Cane Stick Ornaments are a set of four identical foam sticks wrapped in red and off white fabric then covered in glitter for a festive Christmas look. The vintage inspired ornaments are hung from plastic hangers and measure 3.5' high by 0.25" wide.

The Jingles Toy Company Bag Ornament is a tiny version of Santa's toy bag. The checked fabric bag is stuffed and sewn closed with a small mistletoe at the top that adds more holiday cheer to it. A thin string allows the bag to hang while a pinned tag reads Jingle's Toy Co. It was designed by Joyce Napotnik and measures 3" high by 2" wide and 1" deep.

The Nesting Cardinal is a primitive plush cardinal bird glued to a natural twig nest. This adorable piece is a perfect accent to any greenery in your home any time of year. It was designed by Kitty Johnson and measures 2.5" high by 9" wide and 2.5" deep.

The Cardinal Ornament is a primitive fabric cardinal that has been stuffed and hung from a black string for easy display. The cardinal has a moss accent glued to the bottom for the appearance of a nest. It measures 3" high by 5" wide and was designed by Kitty Johnson.

The Janel Doll is a primitive farm girl doll with embroidered facial features, yarn hair tied in a side ponytail, and primitive plush pigs in her arms. Her dress is a bold orange and brown patterned with ivory floral accents and her apron is a simple tan color. Pinned to her chest is a name tag that reads Janel. This doll was designed by Dawn Stake and measures 24" high by 7" wide and 2" deep.

column1: Snowman and Christmas Tree Felt Mat ..
column4: The Snowman and Christmas Tree Felt Mat is a fun way to add holiday cheer to your tables wether it's used as a centerpiece, stand scarf, or even as a placemat. The mat is made of a thick, black felt, and accented by a repeating pattern of ivory snowmen with red scarfs and bright green trees. In the center of the mat is an ivory snowflake. The edges of the mat are scalloped for an added design feature. This mat was designed by Joyce Napotnik and measures 12" in diameter.

column3: (All) The Hearthside Collection|2021 Products|Frames & Table Decor|Halloween|Tabletop
column4: The Ghost and Pumpkin Felt Mat is a festive addition to any Halloween decor wether its used as a centerpiece, stand scarf, or even as a placemat. The mat is made of a thick, black felt, and accented by a repeating pattern of ivory ghosts and orange jack-o-lanterns. The edges of the mat are scalloped for an added design feature. This mat was designed by Joyce Napotnik and measures 12" in diameter.

The Santa Tree Topper is a primitive Santa doll attached to a metal spring used to hold it on to the very top of a tree. This Santa figure has embroidered facial features, a yarn beard, a long red fabric hat and coat, and is carrying a decorated Christmas wreath. The doll also features button eyes, stitched nose and mouth, and a name tag pinned to his collar that reads David. This doll was designed by Kitty Johnson and measures 18" high by 7" wide and 3" deep.

The cane is the classic style of a candy cane and covered in glitter to give it a festive, wintery look.
